title: Bones Wiki

“I don’t know what that means” is a statement frequently uttered by Temperance Brennan . 
Despite Brennan’s extensive knowledge of anthropology, she is quite unaware of pop culture; her co-workers, particularly Agent Booth, like to tease her about it. A running gag on the series is someone making an obvious popular culture reference and she blankly states, “I don't know what that means”, and she is somewhat excited on the rare occasion that she does understand them.
